    "body" : "<p>If your string is potentially <code>null</code>, consider using <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/StringUtils.html#trim-java.lang.String-\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>StringUtils.trim()</code></a> - the null-safe version of <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/String.html#trim()\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>String.trim()</code></a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
