    "body" : "<pre><code>String trimStartEnd = \"\\n TestString1 linebreak1\\nlinebreak2\\nlinebreak3\\n TestString2 \\n\";\nSystem.out.println(\"Original String : [\" + trimStartEnd + \"]\");\nSystem.out.println(\"-----------------------------\");\nSystem.out.println(\"Result String : [\" + trimStartEnd.replaceAll(\"^(\\\\r\\\\n|[\\\\n\\\\x0B\\\\x0C\\\\r\\\\u0085\\\\u2028\\\\u2029])|(\\\\r\\\\n|[\\\\n\\\\x0B\\\\x0C\\\\r\\\\u0085\\\\u2028\\\\u2029])$\", \"\") + \"]\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Start of a string = ^ ,</li>\n<li>End of a string = $ ,</li>\n<li>regex combination = | ,</li>\n<li>Linebreak = \\r\\n|[\\n\\x0B\\x0C\\r\\u0085\\u2028\\u2029]</li>\n</ol>\n"
