    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try this</p>\n<pre><code>function replaceNewLine(str) { \n  return str.replace(/[\\n\\r]/g, &quot;&quot;);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
