    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Another elegant solution.</p>\n<pre><code>String myString = &quot;\\nLogbasex\\n&quot;;\nmyString = org.apache.commons.lang3.StringUtils.strip(myString, &quot;\\n&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2015465,
      "reputation" : 1,
      "user_id" : 1802872,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/552cfaa68c3c890743d976b18a097397?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Juha Saarenp&#228;&#228;",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1802872/juha-saarenp%c3%a4%c3%a4"
    },
